XRTM - X (RT solution method) Radiative Transfer Model

For a description of XRTM and details on building and using the code see the
documentation in either PDF (doc/xrtm.pdf) or HTML format (doc/index.html)

For license information see the file COPYING.

For up-to-date information or to download the latest version of XRTM visit the
XRTM home page at http://reef.atmos.colostate.edu/~gregm/xrtm.

For bugs, comments, or suggestions please email Greg:
greg.mcgarragh@colostate.edu
